---
import aboutImg from "@/assets/about-kesku.png";
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

const meta = {
	description: "I'm Kesku, a tech enthusiast and student. Learn more about me and my interests.",
	title: "About Me, Kesku",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<div class="space-y-6">
		<h1 class="title">About me, Kesku</h1>
		<div class="justify-left flex">
			<Image
				alt="twitter profile picture of Kesku, art is of Usada Pekora from Hololive by @isukash"
				fetchpriority="high"
				loading="eager"
				src={aboutImg}
				style={{ width: "200px", height: "auto" }}
			/>
		</div>
		<sub class="text-center"
			>Art by <a href="https://twitter.com/isukash" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;"
				>@isukash</a
			></sub
		>
		<p>
			I'm UK-based, balancing my studies with my hobbies and life in general. I'm a huge fan of most
			things AI/ML, and I'm always looking for new ways to learn and grow in the field. I'm also a
			huge fan of video games - been playing <a
				href="https://minecraft.net"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">Minecraft</a
			>
			since 2011, and I've been hooked on it ever since. I also play a good amount of
			<a
				href="https://yakuza.sega.com"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">Yakuza</a
			>,
			<a
				href="https://zzz.hoyoverse.com/en-us/"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">Zenless Zone Zero</a
			>,
			<a
				href="https://www.cyberpunk.net"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">Cyberpunk 2077</a
			>, and
			<a
				href="https://www.rockstargames.com/gta-online"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">GTA Online</a
			>
			in my free time.
		</p>

		<h2 class="title">
			"Kesku" is a nickname I've had since I was 15, and it's stuck with me since then.
		</h2>
		<p>It's actually an acronym:</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc">
			<li style="color: #10a7b2;"><strong>K</strong>eep</li>
			<li style="color: #10a7b2;"><strong>E</strong>verything</li>
			<li style="color: #10a7b2;"><strong>S</strong>imple</li>
			<li style="color: #10a7b2;"><strong>K</strong>eep</li>
			<li style="color: #10a7b2;"><strong>U</strong>nderstanding</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			By "Keep Understanding," I mean simplifying concepts so others can grasp them more easily. I believe teaching is one of the best ways to learn, and that's what I'm aiming to do here. Hopefully, I'm presenting things in a clear and understandable way—but I'm still learning, so bear with me!
		</p>
		<p>
			You can find me on <a
				href="https://x.com/yoimnotkesku"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">Twitter</a
			>,
			<a href="https://github.com/kesku" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">GitHub</a>, and
			<a href="https://discordapp.com/users/539468067923820546" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">Discord</a> (<code>kesku</code>). You can also reach out to me via email at <a
				href="mailto:admin@kesku.me" style="color: #10a7b2; text-decoration: underline;">admin@kesku.me</a
			>.
		</p>

		<h2 class="title">What's this blog about?</h2>
		<p>
			Nothing really. Actually, <strong>why are you even here?</strong> I'm just a student who likes
			to write about random stuff. I’m not claiming to be a polished writer—far from it! I’m just here
			to share random words so I look like a professional LMAO - check my twitter for actual information about me.
		</p>

		<p>kes out</p>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
